[package]
name = "cxx-kde-frameworks"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"
links = "cxx-kde-frameworks"

[dependencies]
cxx = "1.0.121"
cxx-qt = "0.7.0"

[build-dependencies]
cmake-package = "0.1.5"

[dependencies.cxx-qt-lib]
features = [ "qt_full",]
version = "0.7.0"

[dependencies.cxx-qt-lib-extras]
version = "0.7.0"

[build-dependencies.cxx-qt-build]
features = [ "link_qt_object_files",]
version = "0.7.0"

[[bench]]
name = "benchmark"
harness = false

[[bench]]
name = "retail_benchmark"
harness = false
required-features = [ "retail_game_testing",]

[package]
name = "physis"
version = "0.4.0"
authors = [ "Joshua Goins <josh@redstrate.com>",]
edition = "2024"
description = "Library for reading and writing FFXIV data."
license = "GPL-3.0"
homepage = "https://xiv.zone/physis"
repository = "https://github.com/redstrate/Physis"
keywords = [ "ffxiv", "modding",]
documentation = "https://docs.xiv.zone/docs/physis/"
readme = "README.md"

[build-dependencies]
system-deps = "7"

[dev-dependencies]
hmac-sha512 = "1"
crc = "3"

[features]
default = [ "visual_data",]
game_install = []
visual_data = [ "dep:half", "dep:bitflags",]
retail_game_testing = []
patch_testing = [ "game_install",]

[dependencies]
quote = "1.0"

[profile.release]
lto = true

[dev-dependencies.brunch]
version = "0.5.3"
default-features = false

[dependencies.binrw]
version = "0.14"
features = [ "std",]
default-features = false

[dependencies.tracing]
version = "0.1"
features = [ "std",]
default-features = false

[dependencies.libz-sys]
version = "1.1"

[dependencies.half]
version = "2"
optional = true

[dependencies.bitflags]
version = "1.3"
optional = true

[package.metadata.system-deps.libunshield]
version = "1.4"
feature = "game_install"

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://invent.kde.org/libraries/cxx-kde-frameworks"]
git = "https://invent.kde.org/libraries/cxx-kde-frameworks"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "master"

[source."https://github.com/redstrate/physis"]
git = "https://github.com/redstrate/physis"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
